               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184710250041"></xptr>
               <p>On the evening of the 7th Oct. I went to lie down in my bed-room—I placed my watch and chain on the table; I slept about two hours—when I awoke they were gone—these are them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
