                  </hi> I am a pawnbroker—I took in this watch and chain of the prisoner on the 7th of Oct.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Was I in a state of intoxication? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No you were not, or I should not have taken it.</p>
