                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, H</hi> 220.) I took the prisoner into custody—he denied it, and said he knew nothing of it, and was as innocent as a child unborn—next morning he said he had stolen the watch, and pawned it in Rateliff-highway.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was drunk when I did it, and when I denied it.</p>
